Aurélien Wiik https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Aur%C3%A9lien_Wiik 0 Aurélien Wiik (born 24 September 1980) is a French actor and filmmaker. He is the son of a Norwegian father and of the French actress Françoise Deldick. Aurélien_Wiik ( born 24_September_1980 ) is a_French_actor_and_filmmaker . He is the_son of a_Norwegian_father and of the_French_actress_Françoise_Deldick .
